## Classic Line Graph 

Overall 


```{r}
fig1 <- ggplot(data = merchTotalMills,
       aes(x = Date,
           y = `Amount (M)`)) +
  geom_line(aes(colour = Type)) +
  labs(title = "Trend of Import/Export, 2020 to 2022") +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))

ggplotly(fig1)
```


