### Import


```{r}
ggplot(data = merchTotalMillsImport,
               aes(x = `Amount (M)`,
                   y = factor(Month, levels = c("Jan", "Feb", "Mar", "Apr", "May", "Jun", "Jul", "Aug", "Sep", "Oct", "Nov", "Dec")),
